                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-36-defend337 t18040111-36-punish230"></join>
               Confined six months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18040111-36-punish231" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040111-36-punish231" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040111-36-punish231" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-36-defend337 t18040111-36-punish231"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Howster, <rs id="t18040111-36-verdict232" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040111-36-verdict232" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 48.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18040111-36-punish233" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040111-36-punish233" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-36-defend339 t18040111-36-punish233"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
